{"tid":2007442,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銅技術涉抄襲 專家嘲淘寶貨","createTime":"2020-05-08T10:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T12:09:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6cbfc618dc8fbf683e7431c4709508e389e0d8ae","tid":2007442,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/OYVVCBWANXNQ3TUIMSSRNMZYB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2FOYVVCBWANXNQ3TUIMSSRNMZYB4%2F&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=7f387fc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2FOYVVCBWANXNQ3TUIMSSRNMZYB4%2F&h=38608083\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/OYVVCBWANXNQ3TUIMSSRNMZYB4/</a><br />\n<br />\n銅技術涉抄襲 專家嘲淘寶貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200508/large/1588870101_55bb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200508%2Flarge%2F1588870101_55bb.gif&h=ff57450e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n專家批評銅芯口罩似淘寶貨。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府宣稱Cu Mask自家研發，耗資八億元，但核心「銅技術」涉嫌抄襲坊間多款可重用銅口罩，港大化學系博士K Kwong指銅口罩是舊有技術，批政府「改少少就當係自己造，如小學生抄功課。」他昨得到銅芯口罩樣本後稱，與淘寶十多元人民幣的布口罩樣式一樣，諷「淘寶搭時光機抄政府」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：高官倘誤導公眾屬行為失當<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市面有多款銅殺菌口罩<br />\n<br />\n市面一直有售以銅殺菌為原理的可重用口罩，如以色列BioBlocX。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n早在2008年已有研究證明銅表面可殺菌，K Kwong指政府如聲稱「發明」這個口罩，「就好似人哋發明咗石燒牛呢個烹飪。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n銅粒子有可能吸入肺部<br />\n<br />\n中科監察潘焯鴻估計，「香港紡織及成衣研發中心2月應該應承咗。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。K Kwong怒轟「有無搞錯？係呃人嘅，銅粒子不論大細都有可能吸入肺部，造成肺纖維化嘅永久傷害。」"},{"pid":"23311b95174da203cf42d3a5aeddf8df43233fb9","tid":2007442,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."},{"pid":"f42645bf57be7f465ee784adc8f5b24dc2a2fd93","tid":2007442,"uid":25363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"肺炎都會搞到肺纖維化<br />\n<br />\n而家戴口罩都有機會令佢纖維化<br />\n<br />\n咁戴黎做咩 慘撚過中肺炎"},{"pid":"360fa04b399cd326c8f666bd2048c2b5e510eabe","tid":2007442,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:34:42.000Z","msg":"樣極衰"},{"pid":"a6ce6b498993ab2f19bd78ccabdf4d9b28efa461","tid":2007442,"uid":181527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"真係派底褲都無咁濕尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d60af113a202f656edbc64d2fad2986f0abe785","tid":2007442,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:09:43.000Z","msg":"咁嘅垃圾洗左8億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買條底褲好過"}]}